$segment4/0 // Speaker 0: Uh, welcome to Ink Cave Presents Readings from the Archive.
$segment4/1 // Speaker 0: I'm Ben Pace.
$segment4/2 // Speaker 0: I'm the host.
$segment4/3 // Speaker 0: Um, on this show, I invite re-writers from the internet who I respect and admire and read, uh, to bring themselves an essay that they read and love, that's dear to their hearts or has influenced them greatly.
